ipei|url=http://focustaiwan.tw/news/aedu/201312120019.aspx|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216173221/http://focustaiwan.tw/news/aedu/201312120019.aspx|archivedate=16 December 2013|publisher=[[Central News Agency (Republic of China)|Central News Agency]]|date=12 December 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 26\n|''[[Asterix & Obelix Take On Caesar]]''\n|France\n|French\n|1999\n|$48,000,000\n|-\n|''[[Thugs of Hindostan]]''\n|India\n|Hindi\n|2018\n|{{H:title|Converted at the 2017 exchange rate of 65.17 INR to 1 USD|<!-- DO NOT ALTER THE FIGURE USED HERE. EXCHANGE RATES FLUCTUATE DAILY AND FOR THIS REASON THIS ARTICLE USES THE AVERAGE ACROSS THE WHOLE OF 2017 WHICH IS THE MOST RECENT YEAR DATA EXISTS FOR. -->$48,000,000}}<ref name=\"thugs\">{{cite web |title=Thugs Of Hindostan - Movie |url=https://boxofficeindia.com/movie.php?movieid=5534 |website=[[Box Office India]] |accessdate=16 December 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|28\n|''[[Asterix & Obelix: Mission Cleopatra]]''\n|France\n|French\n|2002\n|$47,000,000\n|-\n|29\n|''[[Crimson Rivers II: Angels of the Apocalypse]]''\n|France\n|French\n|2004\n|$46,400,000\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |30\n|''[[The Extraordinary Adventures of Ad\u00e8le Blanc-Sec (film)|The Extraordinary Adventures of Ad\u00e8le Blanc-Sec]]''\n|France\n|French\n|2010\n|$46,000,000\n|-\n|''[[Mahavir Karna]]''\n|India\n|Malayalam, Tamil, Hindi\n|2019\n|$46,000,000<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiaglitz.com/mahavir-karna-shooting-started-chiyaan-vikram-r-s-vimal-tamil-news-229131|title=Vikram starts shooting for his multilingual mega epic from today - Tamil Movie News|date=2019-02-08|website=IndiaGlitz.com|access-date=2019-02-10}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thenewsminute.com/article/vikram-commence-work-mahavir-karna-soon-96398|title=Vikram to commence work on 'Mahavir Karna' soon|website=www.thenewsminute.com|access-date=2019-02-10}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tamil/movies/news/vikrams-karna-begins-wit