//www.filmbiz.asia/news/cast-lands-on-three-body-problem|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610090725/http://www.filmbiz.asia/news/cast-lands-on-three-body-problem|url-status=dead|archive-date=June 10, 2015|title=Cast lands on Three Body Problem|author=Kevin Ma|date=April 24, 2015|accessdate=April 24, 2015|work=[[Film Business Asia]]}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" | 81\n|''[[Iceman (2014 film)|Iceman]]''\n|Hong Kong, China\n|Cantonese, Mandarin, Hindi, English, Japanese\n|2014\n|{{H:title|Converted at the 2014 exchange rate of 7.752 HKD to 1 USD|$32,200,000}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jaynestars.com/movies/the-iceman-cometh-3d-lacks-support-from-hong-kong-government/|title=\"The Iceman Cometh 3D\" Lacks Support from Hong Kong Government|author=Addy|date=24 March 2013|accessdate=10 July 2014|work=JaineStars}}</ref>\n|- \n|''[[Tiger Zinda Hai]]''\n|India\n|Hindi, Urdu\n|2017\n|{{H:title|Converted at the 2017 exchange rate of 65.17 INR to 1 USD|$32,200,000}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://boxofficeindia.com/movie.php?movieid=3689|title=Tiger Zinda Hai Movie Review|accessdate=24 January 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|82\n|''[[D-War]]''\n|South Korea\n|English, Korean\n|2007\n|$32,000,000\n|-\n|''[[Lady of the Dynasty]]''\n|China\n|Mandarin\n|2015\n|$32,000,000<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.china.org.cn/arts/2015-08/06/content_36239859.htm|title=Mystery man reshapes 'Lady of the Dynasty' film|author=[[China Daily]]|date=6 August 2015|accessdate=27 November 2015|work=china.org.cn}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Call of Heroes]]''\n|Hong Kong, China\n|Mandarin\n|2016\n|$32,000,000<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.screendaily.com/festivals/filmart/benny-chan-war-epic-casts-up/5085476.article|title=Benny Chan war epic 'The Deadly Reclaim' casts up|first=Liz|last=Shackleton|date=23 March 2015|accessdate=4 April 2016|work=[[Screen Daily]]}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|85\n|''[[Bon Voyage (2003 film)|Bon Voyage]]''\n|France\n|French\n|2003\n|$31,000,000\n|-\n|''[[Sky Fighters]]''\n|France