{"title_page": "1921\u201322 Divizia A", "text_new": "{{Infobox football league season\n| competition = [[Divizia A]]\n| season      = 1921\u201322\n| winners     = [[Chinezul Timi\u0219oara]]<ref>[http://www.romaniansoccer.ro/divizia_a/tables/1921_22.shtml 1921\u201322 Divizia A]</ref>\n| prevseason = [[1920\u201321 Divizia A (Cupa Jean Luca P. Niculescu)|1920\u201321]]\n| nextseason = [[1922\u201323 Divizia A|1922\u201323]]\n}}\n\nThe '''1921\u201322 Divizia A''' was the tenth season of [[Divizia A]], the top-level [[association football|football]] league of [[Romania]].\n\n==Participating teams==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-style=\"background:#ccc;font-weight:bold\"\n|Region || Team\n|-\n| [[Arad, Romania|Arad]]\n| [[AMEF Arad]]\n|-\n| [[Bucharest]]\n| [[Unirea Tricolor Bucure\u0219ti|Tricolor Bucure\u015fti]]\n|-\n| [[Bra\u015fov]]-[[Sibiu]]\n| [[Societatea Sportiv\u0103 Sibiu]]\n|-\n| [[Bukovina]]\n| [[Polonia Cern\u0103u\u0163i]]\n|-\n| [[Cluj-Napoca|Cluj]]-[[Targu Mures|Mures]]\n| [[Victoria Cluj]]\n|-\n| [[Oradea]]\n| [[St\u0103ruin\u021ba Oradea]]\n|-\n| [[Timi\u0219oara]]\n| [[Chinezul Timi\u0219oara]]\n|}\n\n==Final Tournament of Regions==\n\n===Quarters===\n{{OneLegStart}}\n{{OneLegResult|[[Polonia Cern\u0103u\u0163i]]|ROM| 0\u20131 |'''[[Unirea Tricolor Bucure\u0219ti|Tricolor Bucure\u015fti]]'''|ROM|}}\n{{OneLegResult|'''[[St\u0103ruin\u021ba Oradea]]'''|ROM| 2\u20132{{aet}} |'''[[Victoria Cluj]]'''|ROM}}\n{{OneLegResult|[[St\u0103ruin\u021ba Oradea]]|ROM| 0\u20132 |'''[[Victoria Cluj]]'''|ROM}}\n{{OneLegResult|'''[[Chinezul Timi\u0219oara]]'''|ROM| 3\u20130<sup>1</sup> |[[Societatea Sportiv\u0103 Sibiu]]|ROM|}}\n{{end}}\n\n<sup>1</sup> The team from [[Sibiu]] failed to appear, so it lost the game with 0\u20133, by administrative decision.\n\n===Semifinals===\n{{OneLegStart}}\n{{OneLegResult|'''[[Chinezul Timi\u0219oara]]'''|ROM| 2\u20131 |[[AMEF Arad]]|ROM|}}\n{{OneLegResult|'''[[Victoria Cluj]]'''|ROM| 3\u20130<sup>2</sup> |[[Unirea Tricolor Bucure\u0219ti|Tricolor Bucure\u015fti]]|ROM|}}\n{{end}}\n\n<sup>2</sup> The team from [[Bucharest]] failed to appear, so it lost the game with 0\u20133, by administrative decision.\n\n===Final===\n17 September 1922, [[Timi\u0219oara]]\n\n{{OneLegStart}}\n{{OneLegResult|'''[[Chinezul Timi\u0219oara]]'''|ROM| 5\u20131 (2\u20131) |[[Victoria Cluj]]|ROM|}}\n{{end}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Liga I seasons}}<!--\n{{1921\u201322 in Romanian football}}-->\n{{1921\u201322 in European football (UEFA)}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1921-22 Divizia A}}\n[[Category:Liga I seasons]]\n[[Category:1921\u201322 in European association football leagues]]\n[[Category:1921\u201322 in Romanian football]]\n\n\n{{Romania-footy-competition-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football league season\n| competition = [[Divizia A]]\n| season      = 1921\u201322\n| winners     = [[Chinezul Timi\u015foara]]<ref>[http://www.romaniansoccer.ro/divizia_a/tables/1921_22.shtml 1921\u201322 Divizia A]</ref>\n| prevseason = [[1920\u201321 Divizia A (Cupa Jean Luca P. Niculescu)|1920\u201321]]\n| nextseason = [[1922\u201323 Divizia A|1922\u201323]]\n}}\n\nThe '''1921\u201322 Divizia A''' was the tenth season of [[Divizia A]], the top-level [[association football|football]] league of [[Romania]].\n\n==Participating teams==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-style=\"background:#ccc;font-weight:bold\"\n|Region || Team\n|-\n| [[Arad, Romania|Arad]]\n| [[AMEF Arad]]\n|-\n| [[Bucharest]]\n| [[Unirea Tricolor Bucure\u0219ti|Tricolor Bucure\u015fti]]\n|-\n| [[Bra\u015fov]]-[[Sibiu]]\n| [[Societatea Sportiv\u0103 Sibiu]]\n|-\n| [[Bukovina]]\n| [[Polonia Cern\u0103u\u0163i]]\n|-\n| [[Cluj-Napoca|Cluj]]-[[Targu Mures|Mures]]\n| [[Victoria Cluj]]\n|-\n| [[Oradea]]\n| [[St\u0103ruin\u021ba Oradea]]\n|-\n| [[Timi\u015foara]]\n| [[Chinezul Timi\u015foara]]\n|}\n\n==Final Tournament of Regions==\n\n===Quarters===\n{{OneLegStart}}\n{{OneLegResult|[[Polonia Cern\u0103u\u0163i]]|ROM| 0\u20131 |'''[[Unirea Tricolor Bucure\u0219ti|Tricolor Bucure